ted and can be installed automatically. just click \"enable\"\r\nthe rating is also present for all the apps from apps.owncloud.com\r\nis it not working for you?"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/11152952","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/681#issuecomment-11152952","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/681","id":11152952,"user":{"login":"caco3","id":1783586,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/adad2c3132557e364d57c8fc746dd89d?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fd5933a57aa4ee8fb94cdb3f46e14fc32.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"adad2c3132557e364d57c8fc746dd89d","url":"https://api.github.com/users/caco3","html_url":"https://github.com/caco3","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caco3/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caco3/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caco3/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caco3/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caco3/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caco3/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caco3/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caco3/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caco3/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2012-12-08t01:10:38z","updated_at":"2012-12-08t01:10:38z","body":"in the apps menu when i click i.e. on the external app \"journal\", it shows its info and a link to apps.owncloud.org:\r\nhttp://apps.owncloud.com/content/show.php?content=journal\r\nthis link how ever leads to a \"not found\" page on apps.owncloud.org.\r\nthe correct link would be\r\nhttp://apps.owncloud.com/content/show.php?content=154637\r\n\r\ni figured out that the link gets shown correctly, if allow_url_fopen is activated.\r\nalso, if the mentioned option is not enabled, the stars are not shown and the apps get not listed.\r\n\r\nas suggested in https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/329 and https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/487#issuecomment-10677406 i suggest to add a fallback option for curl.\r\n\r\ni am aware that the administration page shows a warning on disabled allow_url_fopen, how ever a normal user will not understand the consequences and get confused about \"not existing\" functions."}]